173 A.3d 599 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. RONALD T. DANIELS, SR., DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-319 Sept.Term 2017

079743 November 14, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003944-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
